[ENGLISH] [CLIC here to see the video montage presentation of my map !](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M2mvOyrFsEM "The video montage presentation of my map !")

Here is the presentation for my first map (Bomb/Defuse) for Counter Strike: Source !
I created this map because I didn't think there were enough maps like this.
I wanted to improve the ammount of objects in CS:S maps, it is futuristic and mysterious without forgetting a military feel.
I optimised the map for a better gameplay feel and for it to be more realistic, I made a few animations for when the bombs explodes (even if it wasn't very important ^^)...
I spent alot of hours on my creation !! (100 hours at least for the map and 20 hours for the video)
I'm of course experienced in these things (maybe a beginner for the video).
This map is a remake of area 51 in the USA but does not have enough buildings for it to be called that.

**>>>> Vote and Share ! Thank you ! <<<<**

  [FRENCH] [CLIQUE ici pour voir le montage de présentation de ma map !](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M2mvOyrFsEM "Le montage de présentation de ma map !")

Voici la présentation de ma toute première map en mode FFA (ou Bomb/Defuse) pour le jeu Counter Strike: Source !
J'ai créer cette map car selon moi il n'existe pas assez de map FFA (cela peux se comprendre car une création de map est quelque chose de long à faire...)
J'ai voulu innover un peu avec par exemple: moins de caisses ; intégration d'objets peu courant dans les maps de CS:S ; une petite immersion "futuriste" et "mystérieuse" sans oublier un environnement restant bien "militaire".
J'ai aussi essayer de pas mal optimisé la map pour une meilleure fluidité en jeu et pour le réalisme j'ai fais pas mal d'animations quand la bombe explose (même si ce n'est pas très important ^^)...
J'ai passez de nombreuses heures sur cette création !! Pour la map: 100 heures minimum et le montage vidéo 20 heures environ...
Bien sûr je ne suis que amateur dans ces deux domaines (un peu débutant même pour le montage).
Cette map rappelle un peu les expériences et secrets de la zone 51 aux USA mais elle ne comporte pas assez de bâtiments et objets extraterrestre pour porter ce nom.

**>>>> Vote et Partage ! Merci ! <<<<**

De_seasideresort_pro is new Counter-Strike: Source map. The map takes place at a luxury hotel. There are many routes inside the building and possibility to flank from outside to the back of the building. Bomb places are located at opposite sides of the building near the center. Terrorists can choose to either stand back on the backyard or try to rush either of the bomb sites. Counter-terrorists can split forces to guard both bomb places or try to hit the terrorists by rushing from center. There are many passageways in the building, which makes it possible to change plans on-the-run. The map is best played with 16 - 64 players. Created by Ghost. Released May 2009. Contact at http://css.setti.info

DE_SEASIDERESORT
----------------

TERRORISTS

You have infiltrated a private club house, the seaside resort for the company chiefs. The place is high quality recreation center. On the other hand, unknown to the public, the place is also bleeding edge gene manipulation facility. You know gene manipulated soy beans are being developed for pig food at the warehouse next to the main building. You don't like gene manipulation.

Your mission is to bomb the experimental soy beans to oblivion. Alternatively you can destroy the research archives at the second floor.


COUNTER-TERRORISTS

You got track of the neo-environmentalists determined to their cause. The research work at the facility is not ideologically contradicting for you. You are sent to the place to prevent the research work being destroyed.

Your mission is to prevent the terrorists from destroying the soy bean test bed and the archives.


Created by: Ghost
Release Date: September 2007
Contact: http://css.setti.info/
Capacity: 16 vs. 16 (32)

**Changes from scud to scud_pro I can remember:**

Mapping/source engine bugs fixed.                   
Better optimization.                            
Updated/added - sounds/textures/decals/models/details.   
Rounded architecture.                                   
Better shadows in map.                                 
Corrected cubemaps.                                  
Fixed bots navigation.                                 
Fixed places where bomb could be lost.                  
Cliped places where you could go off map by boost jump.  
Fixed indefusible bomb exploit at B                    
Corridors are better lit.                             
Fixed "crazy smoke nade" bug at A.                     
Secret room.                                          
Ladder to climb on T balcony's roof.                   
Ladder to climb on bunker's(B) roof                     
Ability to jump on T's balcony with teammates help.      
Easier to jump into bunker(B) through all windows.       
Added lots of interactive objects.                      
One of them is **launchable missiles** at bombsite A.    
Some changes for tactical gameplay.                      

Absence of HDR is intentional.                          
Basic layout of map didn't changed(only added garage at T spawn)                                                
Map is compatible with CS:S nosteam v34                 

**Finaly map is balanced now.**                         
Win ratio was(de_scud):
59.69%(T)/40.31%(CT)                                  
**Win ratio now(scud_pro)**
51.57%(T)/48.43%(CT)

Yes? You? OK... here's a short introduction. Jigsaw ist the bad guy. He kidnaps people, puts them in buildings full of deadly traps and plays his game. The goal is to escape and save your life. de_saw brings you all the locations of the first three movies. There's the bathroom (SAW I), Jigsaw's hideout (SAW I), the trap-house (SAW II) and the old warehouse (SAW III). Furthermore all traps you can see in the movies were recreated. They are fully functional and as deadly as in the movies!
